# Development Preferences for AI Assistants

This file contains key development preferences to be followed by AI assistants when working on this project.

## Design Aesthetics
- NEVER create colored borders around any elements
- Use alternative visual separators: shadows, background changes, spacing, subtle dividers

## Package Management
- ALWAYS use pnpm instead of npm
- Never suggest or use npm commands

## Build Process
- ALWAYS run lint:fix before build
- The prebuild script automatically handles this: `pnpm run build` will run `pnpm run lint:fix` first

## Code Quality
- Create high quality, reusable TypeScript types
- Never use 'any' type
- Follow existing architectural patterns

## Commands Reference
- Development: `pnpm dev`
- Testing: `pnpm test`
- Linting: `pnpm run lint:fix`
- Building: `pnpm run build` (includes automatic lint:fix)

See DEVELOPMENT_GUIDELINES.md for detailed guidelines.
